  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\n*Type*: Bug\r\n\r\n*Summary*: Introduced in https://github.com/status-im/status-react/pull/6722. Messages are shown unread after re-login if i upgrade from release version to nightly.\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\nread messages remain read after relogin\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\nall messages that were read - are marked unread again\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n\r\n- install Status release 0.9.31 from playstore / test flight\r\n- create account\r\n- join some chats (public and 1x1) and have some unread messages\r\n- upgrade to nightly build\r\n- open the app\r\n- read the messages\r\n- logout and login\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n* Status version: nightly 22/11/2018\r\n* Operating System: Android, iOS\r\n",
